\b0 \cf0 \ulnone Now let me share some details about the units in the Minnesota National Guard, and I\'92ll start with our two distinguished Air Guard units. 
\f1 \

\f0 The Air National Guard is a \'91base\'92 oriented force with wings located at both the Minneapolis-St Paul Airport and a base at the Duluth Airport.  
